title: Keemstar: Onision's Real Story is Hidden in Plain Sight
description:
There is evidence that everyone ignored: I speak to "serious hobbyists" who followed the case for years, but seemed to miss this crucial five minutes worth of material, "hidden in plain sight", in the midst of many hours of… controversy.
